       Name: Feint
       Kind: Skill
     Target: TAR_IGNORE
   Position: POS_FIGHTING
   Min Mana: 0
 Wait Beats: 18
 Can Learn: TRUE
Noun Damage:
   Wear-Off: Your feint bonus fades.
Acquisition:
   - Pugilist: level 25
Description:
   Feint sacrifices the current round's attack to set up a powerful
   follow-through. The Pugilist forgoes their immediate action (one
   PULSE_VIOLENCE wait) but gains a hit roll bonus (Pugilist level/4 + 3)
   and an armor class improvement (-Pugilist level/5) for the next 2
   rounds. Best used as a setup move before a high-value strike like
   Pressure Point or Choke Hold to ensure the follow-up lands cleanly.
